## Filter Improvements
Add tag-based filtering to reduce noise:

```go
filter := nostr.Filter{
    Kinds: subscribedKinds,
    Since: nostr.Timestamp(since),
}

// For ContextVM, filter to our pubkey
contextVMFilter := nostr.Filter{
    Kinds: []nostr.Kind{25910, 1059},
    Since: nostr.Timestamp(since),
    Tags:  map[string][]string{"p": {ourPubkey}},
}

// For NIP-78, filter to drydock types
appDataFilter := nostr.Filter{
    Kinds: []nostr.Kind{30078},
    Since: nostr.Timestamp(since),
    Tags:  map[string][]string{"#type": {"ide-session"}},
}
```

